(26, 1, 'SONY XPERIA T 16GB LT30p', 'Gear up with a suavely sophisticated smartphone boasting a best in class rating for both its amazing HD screen and its HD capturing capabilities. This 4G LTE phone is powered by the Android™ platform. ', '​With cutting-edge tech specs fit for a secret agent, the sleek Xperia \r\nLT is capable of handling whatever life throws at you. View everything \r\nin vivid detail on the 4.6" HD Reality Display and say good-bye to \r\njagged edges or hard-to-make-out blurry faces. Be ready to shoot life''s \r\nmost unexpected moments with a 13MP fast capture HD camera that goes \r\nfrom sleep to snap in just over a second and from shot to shot in a \r\nsecond or less. Flip through the "Album" app to rewatch your most recent\r\n adventure in HD, or browse the globe to find that picture you took in \r\nSpain. Use the front facing camera to strike up a face-to-face \r\nconversation in 720p HD and reminisce from miles away. Play and share \r\nyour music, photos and more with other NFC-enabled devices or create \r\none-touch connections with Xperia™ SmartTags to activate a set of \r\nactions with a simple tap1. Share your photos and videos on your HDTV \r\nvia HDMI® while the Xperia TL recharges simultaneously thanks to MHL \r\nsupport. Use your TV remote to browse through your phone''s contents and \r\napps on the TV launcher interface2. Take advantage of your all-access \r\npass to music, movies, games and more. Since them you can access one \r\naccount that makes it easy to stream millions of songs, find your \r\nfavorite TV shows or blockbuster hits.<br><br><b>Fast capture with quick launch</b><br><br>Go from standby to shoot in as little as 1.5 seconds and shot to shot in just about a second with the dedicated camera key.<br><b><br>One-touch connectivity</b><br><br>Create\r\n one-touch connections with NFC. Activate a set of actions using an \r\nXperia™ SmartTag. Play and share your music with other NFC-enabled \r\ndevices. Tap to share photos, music, contacts and more with other \r\ncompatible Xperia smartphones.<br><br><b>Long Term Evolution (LTE)</b><br><br>4G wireless technology that delivers data speeds up to 10X faster than 3G for smartphones.<br><br><b>Mobile BRAVIA® Engine Technology</b><br><br>The\r\n 4.6” HD Reality display powered by Sony’s Mobile BRAVIA® Engine \r\ntechnology makes colors more vivid, enhances contrast and reduces visual\r\n noise.<br><br><b>Sony Entertainment Network</b><br><br>All-access pass \r\nto music, movies, games and more, all through one account. Stream \r\nmillions of songs, watch the latest and classic movies or TV shows.<br><br><b>Exmor® R for mobile</b><br><br>Shoot\r\n high-quality images, even in low light with the Exmor® R for mobile \r\ncamera sensor and 13 megapixel camera. Access up to 25 photo editing \r\noptions with the Album application.<br><br><b>HDMI® with MHL support</b><br><br>Share\r\n all your photos and videos you’ve taken on your HDTV via HDMI®. Charge \r\nyour phone simultaneously with MHL support. Use your TV remote to browse\r\n through your phone’s contents and apps on the TV launcher interface.', NULL, '', '', 'sony-xperia-t-16gb-lt30p', '', '', '', 0),
