(21, 2, 'BlackBerry Curve 9310', '​The BlackBerry Curve 9310 smartphone gives you the full power of BlackBerry in the familiar Blackberry form factor. Experience messaging made easy with a full QWERTY keyboard and real-time chats to friends anywhere in the world with BBM. You’ll love all the great features like the 3.2MP camera, touch-sensitive optical trackpad, GPS, Wi-Fi and apps.', '​<font style="font-size: medium;" face="tahoma, arial, verdana, sans-serif"><span style="font-size: 12px;">​The BlackBerry Curve 9310 smartphone gives you the full power of BlackBerry in the familiar Blackberry form factor. Experience messaging made easy with a full QWERTY keyboard and real-time chats to friends anywhere in the world with BBM. You’ll love all the great features like the 3.2MP camera, touch-sensitive optical trackpad, GPS, Wi-Fi and apps.</span></font><div style="font-family: Simsun; font-size: medium;"><font face="tahoma, arial, verdana, sans-serif"><span style="font-size: 12px;"><br></span></font></div><div style="font-family: Simsun; font-size: medium;"><font face="tahoma, arial, verdana, sans-serif"><span style="font-size: 12px;">The BlackBerry 7.1 OS has new features and pre-installed apps. It makes the whole experience fun and easy with fast, rich web browsing, engaging multimedia, social feeds. It also includes voice-activated universal search with Bing Auto Suggest so you can find what you are looking for hands free.</span></font></div><div style="font-family: Simsun; font-size: medium;"><font face="tahoma, arial, verdana, sans-serif"><span style="font-size: 12px;"><br></span></font></div><div style="font-family: Simsun; font-size: medium;"><font face="tahoma, arial, verdana, sans-serif"><span style="font-size: 12px;"><b>Key Features</b></span></font></div><div style="font-family: Simsun; font-size: medium;"><ul><li><span style="font-size: 12px; font-family: tahoma, arial, verdana, sans-serif;">OS Version: BB7.1</span></li><li><span style="font-size: 12px; font