(24, 2, 'Nokia Lumia 810', 'Enjoy streaming multimedia, making calls, and much more with the Nokia Lumia 810 cell phone. Sporting a 4.3-inch AMOLED ClearBack capacitive multi-touch screen with a resolution of 800x480 pixels, this black Nokia Lumia phone delivers outstanding visual output and simplifies operation.', '<b>​Product Information</b><br><br>Enjoy streaming multimedia, making \r\ncalls, and much more with the Nokia Lumia 810 cell phone. Sporting a \r\n4.3-inch AMOLED ClearBack capacitive multi-touch screen with a \r\nresolution of 800x480 pixels, this black Nokia Lumia phone delivers \r\noutstanding visual output and simplifies operation. Moreover, the 1.5 \r\nGHz dual-core Snapdragon S4 processor incorporated in this smartphone \r\nfacilitates high-speed data processing. Comprising personal information \r\nmanagement tools such as the calendar, clock, and so on, this T-Mobile \r\nNokia Lumia phone helps you organize your tasks. Supporting WLAN IEEE \r\n802.11 a/b/g/n Wi-Fi and Bluetooth 3.0 connectivity, this smartphone \r\nfacilitates wireless communication. You can capture the memorable \r\nmoments of your life with the Nokia Lumia 810 cell phone as it is \r\nequipped with an 8.0 MP camera. What’s more, you can find your way \r\naround unknown regions as this Nokia Lumia phone provides offline maps \r\nand turn-by-turn voice guided navigation.<br><br><b>Product Features</b><br><br><b>Capture, create and share</b><br><br>Advanced\r\n 8 MP camera with Carl Zeiss optics grabs the tough shots. Nokia''s \r\nexclusive Smart Shoot and Panorama features capture faces and broad \r\nvistas with amazing results. Share over Skype, in HD FFC.<br>Make every trip a sure thing<br><br>Be\r\n sure with spoken turn-by-turn directions over Nokia Drive, behind the \r\nwheel or on foot. Bring any destination closer with Nokia Maps and Nokia\r\n Transit, then enjoy the neighborhood with the augmented reality \r\nfeatures of Nokia City Lens local guide.<br><br><b>Designed around you</b><br><br>The\r\n new Windows Phone 8 interface makes this the most intuitive Nokia yet. \r\nScratchproof Corning Gorilla Glass makes the 4.3" OLED WVGA ClearBlack \r\ndisplay as durable as it is beautiful. Great new apps give you more ways\r\n to make your phone your own.<br><br><b>Music to listen, love and share</b><br><br>Nokia\r\n Music gives you virtually unlimited music. Get the latest tracks. \r\nCreate your own channels. Enjoy 150+ channels with over 1,000,000 songs.\r\n Organize and share playlists over social media, stream concerts, buy \r\nand download songs for offline play.<br><br><b>Product Identifiers</b><br><br>Brand&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;Nokia<br>MPN&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;ebay_NokiaLumia810T-MobileBlack<br>Carrier&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;T-Mobile<br>Family Line&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;Nokia Lumia<br>Model&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;810<br>UPC&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;610214630803<br>Type&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;Smartphone<br><br><b>Key Features</b><br><br>Storage Capacity&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;1 GB<br>Color&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;Black<br>Network Generation&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;3G<br>Network Technology&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;GSM<br>Band&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;GSM 850/900/1800/1900<br>Camera&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;8.0 MP<br>Operating System&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;Microsoft Windows Phone 8<br><br><b>Battery</b><br><br>Battery Capacity&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;1650 mAh<br><br><b>Display</b><br><br>Display Technology&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;OLED display<br>Other Features<br>Touch Screen&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;Yes<br>Bluetooth&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;Yes<br>Digital Camera&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;Yes<br>GPS&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;Yes<br>Email Access&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;Yes<br>Internet Browser&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;Yes<br>Speakerphone&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;Yes', NULL, '', '', 'nokia-lumia-810', '', '', '', 0),
(25, 2, 'Nokia Lumia 822', 'One of the biggest advances in the new Lumia 822 is the simplicity that''s built in. The intuitive Windows Phone 8 start screen with live tiles lets you personalize your phone around the way you live. All the apps and features are right at your fingertips.', '​Product Features<br><br><b>Simply irresistible</b><br><br>One of the \r\nbiggest advances in the new Lumia 822 is the simplicity that''s built in.\r\n The intuitive Windows Phone 8 start screen with live tiles lets you \r\npersonalize your phone around the way you live. All the apps and \r\nfeatures are right at your fingertips.<br><br><b>Be a local hero</b><br><br>Top-rated\r\n navigation apps keep you headed in the right direction, even when \r\nyou''re offline. Nokia Drive+ provides turn-by-turn spoken navigation \r\nbehind the wheel. Nokia City Lens augmented reality points out local \r\nattractions in your camera viewfinder. Tap to read reviews, information,\r\n share the location or get directions.<br>Nonstop music, endless choices<br><br>Nokia\r\n Music with Mix Radio make this the music-lover''s smartphone, or will \r\nturn you into one. Free streaming of millions of tracks - no ads, no \r\nlog-in, no sign-up. Download hours of music for offline listening, too.<br><br><b>Snap a photo, make a video</b><br><br>Take\r\n amazing shots using your 8MP camera with industry-leading optics from \r\nCarl Zeiss or capture 1080p HD video. Say it face-to-face using the \r\n1.2MP front-facing camera for video calls. Be sure to download Nokia \r\nLenses, like Smart Shoot and Panaroma from the Windows Phone Store to \r\nget those perfect photos.<br><br><b>Product Identifiers</b><br><br>Brand&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;Nokia<br>MPN&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;ebay_NokiaLumia8221GBVerizonBlack<br><br>Carrier&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;Verizon<br><br>Family Line&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;Nokia Lumia<br>Model&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;822<br>UPC&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;758478025314<br>Type&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;Smartphone<br><br><b>Key Features</b